summary: A small player room for starting characters.
descriptionHtml:
[center][heading][b][size=14][color=#3174d2]Hole in the Wall - Solitude[/color][/size][/b][/heading]
[img]http://i1079.photobucket.com/albums/w503/ytnam/Skyrim/Hole%20in%20the%20Wall%20-%20Solitude/FrontDoor.jpg[/img][/center]A player room with a small amount of storage and an alchemist's table, just outside the gate to Solitude.
Designed for starting new characters, just a small base until you find your feet.
Minimal storage (all safe) and alchemy, with a campfire and cooking available just outside.
All smithing stations and wood chopping available just inside the gates!
Comes with free Solitude guards!
